insights.title: Champion Personality
insights.summary: A mid-lane maverick with explosive potential but inconsistent execution. Your champion pool suggests you love high-impact, mechanically demanding champions that can turn fights on their head.
insights.strength: First Blood Assassin - You've secured 2 first bloods in just 20 matches, showing a killer instinct and early game aggression that catches opponents off guard.
insights.weakness: Consistency is key! Your 40% win rate indicates you're struggling to translate early advantages into game wins. Focus on map awareness, objective control, and maintaining momentum after winning lane.
insights.funFact: Your average game duration of 19 minutes suggests you're either dominating hard or getting dominated - there's no middle ground with you! Embrace the chaos, but learn to channel it strategically.
